comments: Arcidiacono (CHI) makes marginal contact with Rozier (CHA) and doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Rozier (CHA) maintains his pivot foot as he makes the pass.
Biyombo (CHA) makes marginal contact to the lower body of Carter Jr. (CHI) and does not affect his ability to move freely.
LaVine (CHI) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
The Hornets commit a twenty-four second violation.
Biyombo (CHA) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
White (CHI) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) as both players engage and separate during the inbound.
During the pick, Williams (CHA) holds Carter Jr. (CHI) and affects his FOM.
Bridges (CHA) initiates the contact and drives through Carter Jr.'s (CHI) body, who is established in a legal screening position.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bridges (CHA) firms up and absorbs contact.
Rozier (CHA) makes clean hand-on-ball contact to dislodge the ball from Carter Jr. (CHI) on his shot attempt.
Biyombo (CHA) cleanly blocks LaVine's (CHI) shot attempt prior to making incidental contact.
Arcidiacono (CHI) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bridges (CHA) firms up and absorbs the contact.
LaVine (CHI) cleanly dislodges the ball during the inbound pass to Bridges (CHA).
Satoransky (CHI) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA).
White (CHI) dislodges the ball from Graham (CHA) prior to the marginal contact from Arcidiacono (CHI).
